pports campus units with the creation  revision  and assessment of academic programs  The OVPUAAP advises the Vice Chancellor for Academic Affairs and Provost on matters related to strengthening the undergraduate student experience and helping all undergraduates succeed  promoting their well being  on time graduation  and transition to rewarding careers in a constantly changing global society VPUAAP Offices and Programs Helping Students Succeed  n                                  Army ROTC n                n                                  Office of External Fellowships n                n                                  Office of First Year Initiatives n                n                                  Latinos Gaining Access to Networks for Advancement in Science n                n                                  Latin American Recruitment and Educational Services n                n                                  Office for Research on Student Success n                n                                  Office of Undergraduate Research n               Engaging Faculty and Staff  n                                  Office for Advising Development n                n                                  Office of External Fellowships n                n                                  Office of High School Development n                n                                  Office of Project Management for Student Success Initatives n                n                                  Office of Undergraduate Research n               Academic Programs  n                                  Academic Program Review and Assessment n                n                                  Academic Program Development n                n nStudent Success Initatives n  n nStudent Success Initatives n Quick Links   n n nFlag icon n n n n n n n nSummer College n Flag icon  n n nUser icon n n n n n n nL S GANAS n User icon  n n nEnvelope icon n n n n n n n nSummer Sophomore Success Program n En